results.name: G.f.: A(x,y) = exp( Sum_{n>=1} [Sum_{k=0..n} C(n,k)^5 * y^k] * x^n/n ) = Sum_{n>=0,k=0..n} T(n,k)*x^n*y^k, as a triangle of coefficients T(n,k) read by rows.
comment: Compare g.f. to that of the following triangle variants:
example: The logarithm of the g.f. equals the series:
Note that column 1 forms the sum of fourth powers (A000538).
program: (PARI) {T(n, k)=polcoeff(polcoeff(exp(sum(m=1, n, sum(j=0, m, binomial(m, j)^5*y^j)*x^m/m)+O(x^(n+1))), n, x), k, y)}
for(n=0, 10, for(k=0, n, print1(T(n, k), ", ")); print(""))
xref: Cf. variants: A001263 (Narayana), A181143, A181144, A218116.
